==Mandarin==
===Etymology===
Literally: Disease goes in by the mouth and trouble comes out of the mouth.
===Proverb===
{{PAGENAME}} (''[[Pinyin]]'' bìng cóng kŏu rù, huò cóng kŏu chū)
#  Illness comes in via the mouth because of food and trouble goes out via the mouth because of words.
